name: Project share
tagline: A 3rd generation P2P File Sharing Client built as course project using Ruby and Qt
body:
### Welcome to the official website of Project Share!

This webiste contains general documentation and information useful for users and developers of project share file sharing client.

Go ahead and download the source code for the file sharing client, and start contributing to the project share!
